  <entry>
    <title>NOI1-1《编程如此简单—C++程序设计入门》主讲人：朱全民</title>
    <url>/2022/01/25/2/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="NOI1-1《编程如此简单—C-程序设计入门》主讲人：朱全民"><a href="#NOI1-1《编程如此简单—C-程序设计入门》主讲人：朱全民" class="headerlink" title="NOI1-1《编程如此简单—C++程序设计入门》主讲人：朱全民"></a>NOI1-1《编程如此简单—C++程序设计入门》主讲人：朱全民</h2><h3 id="例题：长方形问题"><a href="#例题：长方形问题" class="headerlink" title="例题：长方形问题"></a>例题：长方形问题</h3><p>输入长方形的长l和宽w，计算长方形的周长c和面积s</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">int</span> l,w,c,s;</span><br><span class="line">	cin&gt;&gt;l&gt;&gt;w;</span><br><span class="line">	c=<span class="number">2</span>*(l+w);</span><br><span class="line">	s=l*w;</span><br><span class="line">	cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;周长=&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;c&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">	cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;面积=&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;s&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="练习题：时间计算"><a href="#练习题：时间计算" class="headerlink" title="练习题：时间计算"></a>练习题：时间计算</h3><p>吕布和貂蝉约会，貂蝉迟到了h小时m分钟s秒，请问貂蝉共迟到了多少秒，请编程让计算机回答。</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">int</span> h,m,s;</span><br><span class="line">	cin&gt;&gt;h&gt;&gt;m&gt;&gt;s;</span><br><span class="line">	m=h*<span class="number">60</span>+m;</span><br><span class="line">	s=m*<span class="number">60</span>+s;</span><br><span class="line">	cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;迟到了&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;s&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;秒&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>附件：<br><i class="fa fa-file" aria-hiden="true"></i> <a href="/files/noi/NOI1-1.zip.001">NOI1-1.zip.001</a><br><i class="fa fa-file" aria-hiden="true"></i> <a href="/files/noi/NOI1-1.zip.002">NOI1-1.zip.002</a><br><i class="fa fa-file" aria-hiden="true"></i> <a href="/files/noi/NOI1-1.zip.003">NOI1-1.zip.003</a><br><i class="fa fa-file" aria-hiden="true"></i> <a href="/files/noi/NOI1-1.zip.004">NOI1-1.zip.004</a><br><i class="fa fa-file" aria-hiden="true"></i> <a href="/files/noi/NOI1-1.zip.005">NOI1-1.zip.005</a><br><i class="fa fa-file" aria-hiden="true"></i> <a href="/files/noi/NOI1-1.zip.006">NOI1-1.zip.006</a><br><i class="fa fa-file" aria-hiden="true"></i> <a href="/files/noi/NOI1-1.zip.007">NOI1-1.zip.007</a><br><i class="fa fa-file" aria-hiden="true"></i> <a href="/files/noi/NOI1-1.zip.008">NOI1-1.zip.008</a><br><i class="fa fa-file" aria-hiden="true"></i> <a href="/files/noi/NOI1-1.zip.009">NOI1-1.zip.009</a></p>
]]></content>
